'''''The X-Wing: Rogue Squadron Sourcebook''''' was a [[West End Games]] sourcebook that was due to be published in the Winter of [[1997]]. The book was to be written by [[Eric S. Trautmann]]; there would also be a short story by [[Michael A. Stackpole]]<!--Following detail cannot be verified by the cited source: "detailing [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn's]] experiences at the [[Battle of Bilbringi (9 ABY)|Battle of Bilbringi]]"-->.<ref name="J15">{{JournalCite|15|ISB Intercepts}}</ref>

